SUMMARY:Saturday Night Social Dancing! Salsa EDITION
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Saturday Night Social Dancing! Salsa EDITION \nEvery 2nd Saturday of the month \nSCHEDULE: \n7:00 PM – Class\nStart the night with an engaging dance class led by our instructors. Perfect for both beginners and experienced dancers looking to improve their skills. \n8:00 PM – Guided Practice & Social Dancing\nPut your new moves into action! Our guided practice smoothly transitions into a lively social dance party\, where you can dance\, mingle\, and enjoy the music. \nPRICING:\n– Class: $25 drop-in or $200 for a 10-class package (part of the studio package)\n– Social Dancing: $15 \nWhether you’re here to learn\, practice\, or just enjoy a fun night of dancing\, Saturday Night Social Dancing is the perfect way to spend your evening!
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/saturday-night-social-dancing-salsa-edition/2026-04-11/
LOCATION:Luna Del Soul – House of Dance\, 822 Cassia Street\, Redwood City\, CA\, 94063\, United States
CATEGORIES:San Francisco
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/SNS-Post-2.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Luna Del Soul - House of Dance":MAILTO:info@lunadelsoul.com
END:VEVENT
